# How to Handle Losing at Pickleball

An educational resource provided by the Pickleball Association’s
Emotional Wellness Division.

## Purpose
To promote sportsmanship, emotional regulation, and paddle safety
following unexpected pickleball losses.

## Disclaimer
This site may contain humor.
